social_posts.post_text: A Boy Eats, Vol. 19-21

Happy Valentine’s Day, Aurora ❤️ This picture says a lot about us: we love to laugh, our laughs have merged into one ridiculous laugh, you look gorgeous when you laugh, and I, well, I look like a goat. Here’s to another year of making you laugh. I’m a lucky man. I love you!!!

Happy Birthday to the one and only, Jesa Joy!!! Jesa is responsible for all the amazing merch we made over the past several years. Vlambase would only exist as a simple pun without her. Bonus shout out to the kid Walds and the chicken wing he wouldn’t sacrifice for the pic.
QUASIMODO
This is what directing and acting at the same time looks like. A whole lot of straddling. 📸: @chrislabadie
TOWEL BOY
BEARD BOY
WILLIE F*CKING D!!! Happy birthday, my guy. Here’s looking at you!! FYA
DIRTY VS. DIRTY BLONDE
THE YEAR OF THREES HAS BEGUN - Much love to everyone. Still laughing and feeling like I’m a kid ❤️

HAPPY 3 YEARS GF!!! You haven’t killed me yet, and that’s pretty special. Thank you for recreating our first date with me last night. I know it was cold and the mason jars I used still had a hint of relish in them, but you were a trooper, as always. I’m a lucky man. Here’s to 333 more years together! ❤️ Love, BF
Michael Guerin is adding a stop on his never ending honey moon road trip. See you all in August 👽
Summer’s coming!! Can’t wait for you all to see me, Michael, playing Michael, the AC guy in POOLS 💦 Hats off to the incredible @tori.time for the pic!

Happy Mother’s Day, Mama!!! Words will never be able to describe the feelings I have for you. Thank you for always loving, inspiring, and challenging me. I’m a lucky boy and I have no idea where I’d be without you. I love you so much. Love, Michael ❤️
MAMA’S BOY!!! Happy birthday to my beautiful, incredible mom who somehow gets younger every year ❤️

Happy birthday, Kels!!! I’m beyond proud of you and even though you’re my little sister, I look up to you. You’re one of the smartest people I know. The other smartest person is lil Stephy, who’s absolutely cheesin’ on the right of frame. I’m so lucky to be your big brother and I can’t wait to see what you do next (and not only in work)!!! I love you! Love, Mikey ❤️
Happy Father’s Day to the OG V-Man!!! Thanks for teaching me how to be a man and for never being afraid to wear pink. Love you! ❤️

Happy Birthday, Olive!!! Watching you grow into the beautiful young woman you’ve become has been an absolute joy. You make me and @auroraperrineau such proud parents. Enjoy your day and fart as many times as you’d like!!!

IF YOU LIKE CHEESE, YOU HAVE ABOUT 8 HOURS TO STOCK UP AND GET YOUR DAIRY FILL. SALE ENDS TONIGHT. MICHAELVLAMIS.COM/CHEESE/MORECHEESE/TOOMUCHCHEESE/WHEREHASMYSAGANAKIGONE
HAPPY BIRTHDAY AURORA!!! Here’s to another year of being the Pig to your Nicolas Cage. I love you to the moon you hung and back and can’t wait to continue adventuring with you. Love, Michael ❤️🐷

Every half birthday I like to reflect. I stand in the mirror, reflecting, staring, examining all of the halves that make me whole. I wouldn’t be where I’m at today, standing in the mirror, reflecting, without all of those halves. I encourage you to celebrate your half birthday, or at the very least, celebrate mine. Because you deserve it. And don’t forget, half inches count!! You’re not 5’11”. You’re 5’11” and a half. And that, my friends, is a whole number.

Happy birthday Stephy!!! I’m so proud to be your big brother. I hope your day is as beautiful as you and you get to eat so much delicious food that you pass out and have such bad gas it keeps Jeremy up all night ❤️ Love, Mikey
